OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's politicians have
OL,7,Fbeen reacting to Andy Burnham's
OL,8,Fappointment as Prime Minister.
OL,10,FMr Burnham promised to win over voters
OL,11,F"fed up with politics" and show the
OL,12,Fworld that the UK can once again be a
OL,13,Fsource of stability.
OL,15,FHe used his first speech as Prime
OL,16,FMinister in Downing Street to promise
OL,17,Fto take power out of Westminster and
OL,18,Fgive the public greater control over
OL,19,F"life's essentials".
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@VO]{D@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/17
