OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784647107
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,FSinn Fein MP John Finucane says his
OL,7,Fparty stands ready to "work
OL,8,Fconstructively" with him but that a
OL,9,F"different approach" is needed.
OL,11,FHe added: "Successive British
OL,12,Fgovernment policies and practices have
OL,13,Fbeen devastating for people and
OL,14,Fcommunities and businesses here.
OL,26,@nD@Grr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
