PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784647107
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,F"It's resulted in our public services
OL,7,Fbeing completely undermined and at a
OL,8,Fsecond-class level it's deepened
OL,9,Finequality and I think there's also
OL,10,Fbeen a consistent failure to engage
OL,11,Fwith the Good Friday Agreement in all
OL,12,Fits parts and recognize the fact that
OL,13,Fthere is a very live and active
OL,14,Fconversation with huge momentum around
OL,15,Fthe constitutional future of this
OL,16,Fisland.
OL,18,F"We will be engaging with Andy Burnham
OL,19,Fon all of these matters and we look
OL,20,Fforward to doing so."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
