PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784647107
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,FShe said: "What we need to see from
OL,7,FAndy Burnham is actually facilitating
OL,8,Fthis process to get round the table,
OL,9,Fto get a budget agreed and delivered,
OL,10,Fbut most importantly to make sure that
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland is funded at need.
OL,13,F"We can't possibly keep doing this. We
OL,14,Fcannot keep throwing good money after
OL,15,Fbad into a situation and a form of
OL,16,Fgovernment that we know needs reform.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784647107
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,F"Andy Burnham has said that he's all
OL,7,Fabout devolution. He's said that he's
OL,8,Fall about delivering for local places,
OL,9,Fhe needs to listen to people in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland whenever we tell him,
OL,11,Fand the public, more importantly,
OL,12,Ftells him that we need reform of
OL,13,FStormont, and he needs to get on and
OL,14,Fdeliver that for us."
OL,16,FUUP MP Robin Swann says Mr Burnham
OL,17,Fneeds to match his rhetoric with
OL,18,Fdelivery for the United Kingdom.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784647107
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,F"What I want to see is actually how he
OL,7,Fstarts to put what he's saying into
OL,8,Faction. It's fine talking about hope
OL,9,Fand talking about change at an
OL,10,Felection because there you can
OL,11,Fengender that, that hope, that ability
OL,12,Fto change.
OL,14,F"We're two years into this Labour
OL,15,Fgovernment. We're two years into this
OL,16,Fmanifesto that he's still saying he's
OL,17,Fgoing to honour.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784647107
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,F"What I want to see is how he's going
OL,7,Fto be different from the last one, how
OL,8,Fhe's going to be able to deliver the
OL,9,Fthings that Keir Starmer said he was
OL,10,Fgoing to deliver but wasn't able to
OL,11,Fbecause the money wasn't there. So
OL,12,Fwhere does Andy Burnham as Prime
OL,13,FMinister actually get the finances,
OL,14,Fthe political support, and the
OL,15,Finternational credibility to do what
OL,16,Fhe wants to do?
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784647107
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,F"I wish him well. I want to see this
OL,7,Fgovernment succeed. I want to see the
OL,8,FUnited Kingdom succeed, but, I think
OL,9,Fthere's a big challenge in front of
OL,10,Fhim."
OL,12,FClaire Hanna congratulated Mr Burnham
OL,13,Fbut warned he faces major challenges.
OL,15,F"It will be a short honeymoon," she
OL,16,Fsaid, adding people "want change that
OL,17,Fisn't coming as fast as it might do".
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@_O]xD@UOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
