CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784647107
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,FThe SDLP leader said: "People's
OL,7,Fcynicism has grown about what politics
OL,8,Fcan and will do, so Andy Burnham does
OL,9,Fneed to make some tangible changes.
OL,11,F"He is dealing with the same
OL,12,Fimbalanced UK economy, he is dealing
OL,13,Fwith the same existential challenge
OL,14,Fthat the UK is having about who is it
OL,15,Fand where it fits in the world, he is
OL,16,Fdealing with increased political
OL,17,Fpolarisation in Britain.
OL,26,@nD@WOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784647107
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,F"As regards this region, the fact is
OL,7,Four budget process is so chaotic,
OL,8,Fthere is so little responsibility
OL,9,Ftaking by Executive parties, in years
OL,10,Fwhen we are well funded, it's in short
OL,11,Fterm trenches or money, a collapse
OL,12,Fhere, a crisis there, a side deal,
OL,13,Frather than a degree of clarity for
OL,14,Fpublic services and what they can do.
OL,16,F"We will want the UK government to
OL,17,Ftake a more strategic approach, but
OL,18,Fthat will also include the Executive
OL,19,Fparties accepting that they sought and
OL,20,Fwon power at the ballot box, and that
OL,21,Falso means running the place."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
