OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,FThe carefully choreographed handover
OL,7,Fof power came after Sir Keir Starmer
OL,8,Fhad his own audience with the King to
OL,9,Fformally resign.
OL,11,FIn his final appearance in Downing
OL,12,FStreet, Sir Keir said "my work is
OL,13,Fdone" and he was leaving the country
OL,14,F"stronger and fairer" than when he
OL,15,Ftook office just two years ago.
OL,17,FThe Taoiseach was among the
OL,18,Finternational leaders who have
OL,19,Fcongratulated Andy Burnham on becoming
OL,20,FPrime Minister.
OL,26,@tD@WOUuD@EO]vD@AOUvD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
