OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784647107
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,FMicheal Martin said Mr Burnham was "a
OL,7,Fgreat champion of deeper links between
OL,8,FIreland and Britain".
OL,10,FIn a statement, he added: "I look
OL,11,Fforward to working with him to further
OL,12,Fstrengthen the partnership and
OL,13,Ffriendship between our two countries.
OL,15,F"Our relationship has deepened further
OL,16,Fin recent years with annual UK-Ireland
OL,17,Fsummits, and our respective roles as
OL,18,Fco-guarantors of the Good Friday
OL,19,FAgreement.
OL,26,@nD@FrpnD@dOUpD@TO]rD@[OUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784647107
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,F"We will also work to facilitate a
OL,7,Fstronger relationship between the UK
OL,8,Fand European Union.
OL,10,F"I will work with Prime Minister
OL,11,FBurnham to ensure that close co-
OL,12,Foperation between Ireland and the UK
OL,13,Fdelivers real tangible benefits for
OL,14,Fpeople, communities and businesses
OL,15,Fright across these islands."
OL,17,FThe Taoiseach said he knew the Prime
OL,18,FMinister from "previous meetings" when
OL,19,FMr Burnham was mayor of Greater
OL,20,FManchester.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@\O]zD@OOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
