PN,41716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784647107
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,FHe said: "He came to Ireland on a
OL,7,Fnumber of occasions and also, of
OL,8,Fcourse, when we met at the Anglo-Irish
OL,9,FSummit in Liverpool the year before
OL,10,Flast.
OL,12,F"We will work closely with him. We are
OL,13,Fco-guarantors of the Good Friday
OL,14,FAgreement, and we look forward to
OL,15,Fcontinuing the very good relationship
OL,16,Fwe had with Keir Starmer and this
OL,17,Fgovernment in terms of the Good Friday
OL,18,FAgreement, the joint framework
OL,19,Fdeclaration on legacy, and that we can
OL,20,Fprogress the legislation.
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
