PN,41717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784647107
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland politicians react as
OL,4,CBurnham becomes Prime Minister
OL,6,F"Also then in the context of the
OL,7,FEuropean Union, that we can work to
OL,8,Ffacilitate a stronger and warmer
OL,9,Frelationship between the United
OL,10,FKingdom and the European Union ` and I
OL,11,Fthink we've made good progress on that
OL,12,Ffront."
